<div class="quote-block">
<p><em>Following a tip-off to a Foundation Site, <a href="/task-forces#mu-13">Mobile Task Force Mu-13</a> (&quot;Ghostbusters&quot;) was alerted to the nearest Mindscape nexus gate and commenced a raid at the conceptual corner of Surreptitious and Scrumptious. At the supposed location of Ambrose Mindscape, no conscious activity was detected.</em></p>
